		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">At 7th level, you learn how to temporarily take on the form of an elemental. You can cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.95tar7xr3hdp0o92]{Polymorph} on yourself without expending any spell points, except only to turn into an air, earth, fire, or water elemental, matching your element. Once you use this ability, you must complete a long rest before you can use it again. While transformed this way, you can only cast spells matching the element whose form you have taken, and you can use your&nbsp;@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.uit7l3mc64l5h8h1]{Elemental Blast} and @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.rosj8xvi8bstdegy]{Control Elements} abilities.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At 15th level, you can instead turn into a giant air, earth, fire, or water elemental.</p>",
